An,SMS,API,for,mobile,marketing,campaigns,Use,this,API,as,part,of,a,cost,effective,flexible,private,label,solution,Possible,uses,are,campaigns,real,time,alerts,interactive,displays,site,integration,or,customer,support,classifieds,and,real,estate,Send,messages,to,certain,phone,numbers,If,the,message,is,over,characters,the,message,will,be,broken,into,parts,automatically,You,also,can,schedule,messages,and,specify,a,time,zone,for,them,Cancel,scheduled,messages,as,needed,Enter,a,message,ID,and,learn,its,delivery,status